    "searchText": "纽约王 美国 电影 2024 犯罪, 剧情 黑帮, 复仇, 权力游戏, 纽约 刚刚出狱的黑帮老大发现自己的帝国被瓜分，他决定用最血腥的方式重新夺回王座。 serving a 25-year sentence, vincent “the king” morello returns to a new york city he barely recognizes. his once-feared crime family has been dismantled, his territories seized by a coalition of russian mobsters and a corrupt real estate mogul. refusing a quiet retirement, vincent assembles a small crew of loyal old-timers and disillusioned young outsiders. he doesn’t just want his empire back; he wants to reshape the rules of the game. using a blend of old-school brutality and surprising strategic cunning, he plays the rival factions against each other. the story follows his meticulous, bloody ascent as he confronts not only his enemies but also the ghosts of his past, ultimately questioning what “king” even means in a city that has left him behind. 悬疑犯罪"
